	(text_box "NOTE:\n\nThis module is designed to better display up to three digital signals originating from a source with moderately high output impedance (a few hundred ohms) to a visualizer or oscilloscope with moderately high input capacitance (tens of picofarads).\n\nThis module supports a maximum frequency of approximately 50MHz at 5V, which decreases to 10MHz at 1.8V."
